column16: Carlos Gomez lines out sharply to third baseman Chase Headley.
Evan Gattis pops out to shortstop Didi Gregorius.
Colby Rasmus grounds out, second baseman Stephen Drew to first baseman Greg Bird.
Carlos Correa flies out to right fielder Chris Young.
Chris Carter lines out sharply to third baseman Chase Headley.
Jake Marisnick singles on a ground ball to left fielder Brett Gardner.   Marwin Gonzalez to 2nd.
Jason Castro flies out to left fielder Brett Gardner.
Marwin Gonzalez singles on a sharp ground ball to second baseman Stephen Drew, deflected by first baseman Greg Bird.
